  "excerpt": "We are always trying to make small improvements to the club, and some of you may have noticed our most recent change &#8211; new TVs by the doubles court in the lounge area and in the fitness room, and a cable TV connection. Thank you to Travis Chapman for sponsoring the new TV in the &#8230; Read more",
  "content": "<p>We are always trying to make small improvements to the club, and some of you may have noticed our most recent change &#8211; new TVs by the doubles court in the lounge area and in the fitness room, and a cable TV connection.</p>\n<p><div id='gallery-4' class='gallery galleryid-3058 gallery-columns-2 gallery-size-large'><figure class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<div class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/cable-tv-is-now-live-at-the-squash-club/loungetvpic3/#main'><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/LoungeTVpic3.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/LoungeTVpic3.jpeg 800w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/LoungeTVpic3-300x225.jpeg 300w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/LoungeTVpic3-20x15.jpeg 20w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</div></figure><figure class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<div class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/cable-tv-is-now-live-at-the-squash-club/loungetvpic2/#main'><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/LoungeTVpic2.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/LoungeTVpic2.jpeg 800w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/LoungeTVpic2-300x225.jpeg 300w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/LoungeTVpic2-20x15.jpeg 20w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</div></figure>\n\t\t</div>\n</p>\n<p>Thank you to  Travis Chapman for sponsoring the new TV in the Lounge area and to Jim Dawson at  Thinktel for donating a TV for the Fitness Room and coordinating the Shaw Cable. Thank you also to Marc Moreau for mounting the lounge TV.</p>\n<p><div id='gallery-5' class='gallery galleryid-3058 gallery-columns-2 gallery-size-large'><figure class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<div class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/cable-tv-is-now-live-at-the-squash-club/exercise-room-tv/#main'><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"600\" height=\"402\" src=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/exercise-room-TV.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/exercise-room-TV.jpg 600w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/exercise-room-TV-300x201.jpg 300w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/exercise-room-TV-20x13.jpg 20w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</div></figure><figure class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<div class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/cable-tv-is-now-live-at-the-squash-club/fitness-room-eliptical/#main'><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"600\" height=\"402\" src=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/fitness-room-eliptical.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/fitness-room-eliptical.jpg 600w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/fitness-room-eliptical-300x201.jpg 300w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/fitness-room-eliptical-20x13.jpg 20w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</div></figure>\n\t\t</div>\n</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
